  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The SAS registry will include any patient with previous coronary stenting undergoing any type
      of surgery or operative endoscopic/endovascular procedure at the participating Centers. The
      relevant clinical, procedural and outcome data (within index surgical admission and at 30
      days) will be entered in a specifically designed electronic case record form (eCRF).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
